(42, 22, 34, 40, 26, 34, 34, NULL, 'Denial Prophecy Connection', 'Both passages emphasize Peter''s denial of Jesus occurring before the cock crows. They highlight the specific prediction of Peter denying Jesus thrice, establishing a direct link between the two accounts.', 'prophecy', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
