(42, 22, 34, 40, 26, 74, 74, 'the cock shall not crow', 'Peter''s Denial and the Rooster', 'This connection highlights Peter''s denial of Jesus as foretold in Luke 22:34 and its fulfillment in Matthew 26:74. Both passages emphasize the moment of denial occurring just before the rooster crows.', 'prophecy', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
