(42, 22, 36, 52, 2, 14, 15, NULL, 'Persecution and Preparation for Suffering', 'This connection highlights the theme of preparation for suffering and conflict. In Luke, the instruction to acquire a sword suggests readiness for impending challenges, while in 1 Thessalonians, the mention of suffering reflects the reality of persecution faced by believers.', 'theme', 0.286, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 22, 36, 52, 3, 4, 4, NULL, 'Preparation for Suffering', 'This connection highlights the theme of preparation for impending challenges. In Luke 22:36, the instruction to acquire a sword suggests readiness for conflict, while 1 Thessalonians 3:4 emphasizes the forewarning of suffering tribulation.', 'theme', 0.286, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 22, 36, 60, 4, 1, 1, NULL, 'Preparation for Suffering', 'This connection highlights the theme of preparation for trials. In Luke 22:36, the instruction to arm oneself with a sword parallels 1 Peter 4:1''s call to arm oneself with the same mind as Christ, emphasizing readiness for suffering.', 'theme', 0.27899999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 22, 37, 23, 53, 12, 12, 'he was reckoned among the transgressors', 'Connection of Transgressors Theme', 'Both passages emphasize being ''numbered with the transgressors,'' highlighting a shared theme of suffering and sacrifice. This connection underscores the fulfillment of prophecy regarding the Messiah''s role in bearing sin.', 'theme', 0.496, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
