(42, 22, 37, 48, 3, 13, 13, 'reckoned among the transgressors', 'Connection of Curses and Transgressors', 'This connection highlights the theme of Christ''s identification with transgressors and the curse associated with sin. Both passages emphasize the fulfillment of scripture regarding Christ''s suffering and the consequences of the law.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
